Package nl.naturalis.common.collection

Class UnmodifiableTypeMap.Builder<V>

java.lang.Object
nl.naturalis.common.collection.UnmodifiableTypeMap.Builder<V>
Type Parameters:
V -
Enclosing class:
UnmodifiableTypeMap<V>
public static final class UnmodifiableTypeMap.Builder<V>
extends Object
A Builder class that lets you add types one by one without having to pay attention to the order in which you add them. Once you call freeze() on the Builder, it will make sure the types enter the TypeMap in the right order (lowest-level classes first, base classes and interfaces last).
Author:
Ayco Holleman
